    "title": "Senior Teacher - Quest Alliance - Attractive Package",
    "description": "Join the Quest Alliance family as a Senior Teacher in Delhi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Quest Alliance:\nQuest Alliance is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Quest Alliance!",
